Get Foreign Key Columns


To get all foreign key columns of all foreign key constraints in a table:


var fkMap  = db.get('public.product').foreignKeyColumns; // Map { color_id =
 Column {}, vendor_id =
 Column {}  }




To get foreign key columns of a specific constraint:


var fkMap  = db.get('public.product').foreignKeyConstraints.get('vendor_has_products').columns; // Map { vendor_id =
 Column {} }




